1 November 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Onur Air]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Antalya Airport|Antalya]],<ref name=\"Coral\">{{cite web|url=https://www.coraltravel.pl/rozklad-lotow|title=Coral Travel|publisher=coraltravel.pl}}</ref> [[Milas\u2013Bodrum Airport|Bodrum]]<ref name=\"Coral\"/>\n<!-- -->\n|[[Ryanair]]| [[Alicante\u2013Elche Airport|Alicante]], [[Beauvais-Till\u00e9 Airport|Beauvais]], [[Orio al Serio International Airport|Bergamo]], [[Bologna Guglielmo Marconi Airport|Bologna]], [[Bristol Airport|Bristol]], [[Brussels South Charleroi Airport|Charleroi]], [[Cork Airport|Cork]], [[Dublin Airport|Dublin]], [[East Midlands Airport|East Midlands]], [[Edinburgh Airport|Edinburgh]], [[Gda\u0144sk Lech Wa\u0142\u0119sa Airport|Gda\u0144sk]], [[Glasgow Airport|Glasgow]], [[Boryspil International Airport|Kiev\u2013Boryspil]], [[Leeds Bradford Airport|Leeds/Bradford]], [[Liverpool John Lennon Airport|Liverpool]], [[London Stansted Airport|London\u2013Stansted]], [[Malta International Airport|Malta]], [[Manchester Airport|Manchester]], [[Naples International Airport|Naples]], [[Newcastle International Airport|Newcastle upon Tyne]], [[Odesa International Airport|Odessa]], [[Palermo Airport|Palermo]], [[Ciampino\u2013G. B. Pastine International Airport|Rome\u2013Ciampino]], [[Sandefjord Airport, Torp|Sandefjord]], [[Shannon Airport|Shannon]]<br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Athens International Airport|Athens]], [[Cagliari\u2013Elmas Airport|Cagliari]] (begins 3 April 2020),<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fly4free.pl/nowa-trasa-ryanair-z-polski/|title=2 nowe wakacyjne trasy Ryanaira z Polski! Polecimy do W\u0142och!|website=Fly4free.pl - tanie loty i sposoby na tanie bilety lotnicze|accessdate=Mar 7, 2020}}</ref> [[Chania International Airport|Chania]], [[Corfu International Airport|Corfu]] (begins 4 June 2020),<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://corporate.ryanair.com/news/ryanair-launches-new-corfu-route-to-wroclaw-for-summer-2020/|title=Ryanair Launches New Corfu Route To Wroclaw For Summer 2020 &#124; Ryanair's Corporate Website|accessdate=Mar 7, 2020}}</ref> [[Faro Airport|Faro]], [[Girona\u2013Costa Brava Airport|Girona]], [[Adolfo Su\u00e1rez Madrid\u2013Barajas Airport|Madrid]], [[M\u00e1laga Airport|M\u00e1laga]], [[Palma de Mallorca Airport|Palma de Mallorca]], [[Podgorica Airport|Podgorica]], [[Tenerife South Airport|Tenerife\u2013South]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Scandinavian Airlines]]| '''Seasonal:''' [[Copenhagen Airport|Copenhagen]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Smartwings Poland]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Milas\u2013Bodrum Airport|Bodrum]] (begins 4 June 2020),<ref name=\"TUI.pl\"/> [[Chania International Airport|Chania]] (begins 26 April 2020),<ref name=\"itaka.pl\">{{cite web|url=https://biletylotnicze.itaka.pl/|title=air and charter tickets|website=itaka.pl}}</ref> [[Corfu International Airport|Corfu]] (begins 25 April 2020),<ref name=\"itaka.pl\"/> [[Lamezia Terme International Airport|Lamezia Terme]] (begins 7 June 2020),<ref name=\"itaka.pl\"/> [[Rhodes International Airport|Rhodes]] (begins 24 April 2020)<ref name=\"itaka.pl\"/>\n<!-- -->\n| [[SunExpress]] | '''Seasonal:''' [[\u0130zmir Adnan Menderes Airport|\u0130zmir]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sunexpress.com/en/ |title=Book cheap flights online to Turkey, Egypt, Bulgaria, Scandinavia and Canary Islands |publisher=sunexpress.com |date= |accessdate=2019-05-10}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n|{{nowrap|[[Swiss International Air Lines]]}} | [[Z\u00fcrich Airport|Z\u00fcrich]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Wizz Air]]| [[Birmingham Airport|Birmingham]], [[Doncaster Sheffield Airport|Doncaster/Sheffield]], [[Dortmund Airport|Dortmund]], [[Eindhoven Airport|Eindhoven]], [[Kharkiv International Airport|Kharkiv]], [[Kiev International Airport (Zhuliany)|Kiev\u2013Zhuliany]], [[David the Builder Kutaisi International Airport|Kutaisi]], [[Luton Airport|London\u2013Luton]], [[Lviv Danylo Halytskyi International Airport|Lviv]], [[Odesa International Airport|Odessa]], [[Keflavik Airport|Reykjav\u00edk\u2013Keflav\u00edk]], [[Sandefjord Airport, Torp|Sandefjord]], [[Stockholm Skavsta Airport|Stockholm\u2013Skavsta]], [[Zaporizhia International Airport|Zaporizhia]] <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kyivpost.com/business/wizz-air-launches-6-flights-from-zaporizhia-in-march-2020.html|title=Wizz Air launches 6 flights from Zaporizhia in March 2020 {{!}} KyivPost - Ukraine's Global Voice|date=2019-10-22|website=KyivPost|access-date=2019-10-22}}</ref> <br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Bari Karol Wojty\u0142a Airport|Bari]]\n<!-- -->\n}}\n\n==Statistics==\n[[File:Terminal T2 we Wroc\u0142awiu - landside.jpg|thumb|Interior of Main Terminal]]\n[[File:Airport in Wroclaw.jpg|thumb|General Aviation Terminal]]\nFollowing are the official airport annual traffic figures.<ref>[http://www.ulc.gov.pl/_download/regulacja_rynku/statystyki/liczba_obsl_pasazerow_przesylek_20042007_150208.pdf \"Annual statistics\"], ''ulc.gov.pl. Link accessed 2012-05-28.</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Passengers\n! Cargo (tonnes)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://airport.wroclaw.pl/lotnisko/o-lotnisku/statystyki/cargo/|title=Cargo - Port Lotniczy Wroc\u0142aw|website=airport.wroclaw.pl}}</ref>\n! Movements\n|- align=right\n! 1998\n| 174 202\n| 871\n| 9 558\n|- align=right\n! 1999\n| 191 502\n| 628\n| 10 333\n|- align=right\n! 2000\n| 210 873\n| 2 548\n| 11 858\n|- align=right\n! 2001\n| 237 705\n| 1 172\n| 7 430\n|- align=right\n! 2002\n| 236 151\n| 1 571\n| 6 594\n|- align=right\n! 2003\n| 284 334\n| 1 183\n| 12 384\n|- align=right\n! 2004\n| 355 431\n| 823\n| 18 509\n|- align=right\n! 2005\n| 454 047\n| 1 378\n| 20 556\n|- align=right\n! 2006\n| 857 931\n| 1 510\n| 25 002\n|- align=right\n! 2007\n| 1 270 825\n| 1 458\n| 26 948\n|- align=right\n! 2008\n| 1 486 442\n| 1 462\n| 32 000\n|- align=right\n! 2009\n| 1 365 456\n| 1 031\n| 25 472\n|- align=right\n! 2010\n| 1 654 439\n| 946\n| 23 627\n|- align=right\n! 2011\n| 1 657 472\n| 957\n| 25 339\n|- align=right\n! 2012\n| 1 996 552\n| 928\n| 27 960\n|- align=right\n! 2013\n| 1 920 1